parameters.name: AcceleratorId
parameters.description: The ID of the GA instance.

parameters.name: EndpointGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the endpoint group.

parameters.name: FromPort
parameters.description:
The start port of the backend service port range of the endpoint group.

Valid values: **1** to **65499**. The **FromPort** value must be smaller than or equal to the **ToPort** value.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Maximum value: **50**. Default value: **10**.

parameters.name: Protocols
parameters.description:
The backend service protocols of the endpoint group. Valid values:

- **TCP**: TCP.
- **UDP**: UDP.
- **TCP,UDP**: TCP and UDP.

If this parameter is empty, all types of protocols are queried.

You can specify up to 10 protocols.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the GA instance. Set the value to **cn-hangzhou**.

parameters.name: ToPort
parameters.description:
The end port of the backend service port range of the endpoint group.

Valid values: **1** to **65499**. The **FromPort** value must be smaller than or equal to the **ToPort** value.
